FBIS3-41271 "jptdd007__l94061" JPRS-TDD-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 14 February 1994 EAST EUROPE BULGARIA Police Seize Heroin, Arrest Six Iranians AU1002070894 Sofia BTA in English 2019 GMT 9 Feb 94 AU1002070894 Sofia BTA Language: English Article Type:BFN ["Today"--BTA lead] [Excerpts] Sofia, February 9 (BTA) -- The police found 100 g of heroin and six illegal aliens--citizens of Iran, in a weekend house in the vicinity of the St. Konstantin Black Sea resort February 8, BTA was told by Col. Angel Denev, spokesman for the regional directorate of the interior in Varna, northeastern Bulgaria. Investigative proceedings were initiated against two of the Iranians. [passage omitted]
